title: 'SuperThins (and not pure cotton)'
body: 'These are super thin: so good when you really don\'t want much on your feet.  But they don\'t feel like cotton more like acrylic: and the Elastic at the knee/shin don\'t look like they\'ll last.  Buy if you really want "thin" socks but don\'t want the ankle-lenth versions.'

title: 'Great socks and long lasting'
body: 'This is the second time i have ordered this socks. The last pair was ordered 3 years back !  Extremely good quality and great fabric!'

title: 'Thumb up'
body: Little long than expected It's ok Comfortable n soft

title: 'Socks'
body: 'Shrink after a wash. Loss of money'
